headline: Queen Mary 2 to join America's 250th anniversary celebration in New York in 2026 as Cunard partners with Sail4th 250
summary: Cunard today announced an exciting partnership with Sail4th 250, the non-profit organization overseeing celebrations in the Port of New York and New Jersey for America's 250th anniversary next year.

headline: How Private Islands Are Reshaping the Cruise Industry
summary: Major cruise lines are leasing private islands and beaches in the Bahamas, keeping spending within their own ecosystems. But some question whether it benefits host nations or takes business away from local ports.
